        <item>
            <title>iPhone SE 4 變成「最遲下週」到來？但蘋果還有些「小發表」會在本週公開</title>
            <description>&lt;figure class=&quot;caas-figure&quot;&gt;&lt;div class=&quot;caas-figure-with-pb&quot;&gt;&lt;div&gt;&lt;div class=&quot;caas-img-container&quot;&gt;&lt;img class=&quot;caas-img has-preview&quot; alt=&quot;iPhone SE 4 變成「最遲下週」到來？但蘋果還有些「小發表」會在本週公開&quot; src=&quot;https://s.yimg.com/os/creatr-uploaded-images/2025-01/619af150-dd93-11ef-9fba-eac81d0d58ca&quot; referrerpolicy=&quot;no-referrer&quot;&gt;&lt;/div&gt;&lt;/div&gt;&lt;/div&gt;&lt;div class=&quot;caption-wrapper caption-aligned-with-image&quot;&gt;&lt;figcaption class=&quot;caption-collapse&quot;&gt;iPhone SE 4 變成「最遲下週」到來？但蘋果還有些「小發表」會在本週公開&lt;/figcaption&gt;&lt;/div&gt;&lt;/figure&gt;&lt;p&gt;彭博的 Mark Gurman 在其最新的推文中提到，原本可能「本週」登場的 iPhone SE 4 現在變成了「最遲下週」亮相。盡管如此，蘋果仍是有一些「小發表」會在本週公開。其中第一個消息可能今天晚些時候就會公佈，但暫不清楚和什麼有關。而在週五似乎會有和 Vision Pro 相關的新聞，據稱蘋果的 PR 已經在聯絡媒體。&lt;/p&gt;&lt;div class=&quot;twitter-tweet-wrapper&quot; data-embed-anchor=&quot;0246377d-37e8-581e-9df9-e795e52b3bbf&quot;&gt;&lt;blockquote placeholder=&quot;&quot; data-theme=&quot;light&quot; class=&quot;twitter-tweet&quot;&gt;&lt;div class=&quot;caas-card-loader small fixed-height&quot;&gt;&lt;/div&gt;&lt;p&gt;New iPhone SE is still imminent and should be announced by next week, when the company is holding product briefings. Tomorrow there’s a smaller announcement. For Friday, Apple Vision Pro reps are reaching out to press about an announcement to come. M4 MacBook Air within weeks. &lt;a href=&quot;https://t.co/UabWO0shjY&quot; rel=&quot;nofollow noopener&quot; target=&quot;_blank&quot; data-ylk=&quot;slk:https://t.co/UabWO0shjY;elm:context_link;itc:0;sec:content-canvas&quot; class=&quot;link &quot;&gt;https://t.co/UabWO0shjY&lt;/a&gt;&lt;/p&gt;&lt;p&gt;— Mark Gurman (@markgurman) &lt;a href=&quot;https://twitter.com/markgurman/status/1889504630507446454?ref_src=twsrc%5Etfw&quot; rel=&quot;nofollow noopener&quot; target=&quot;_blank&quot; data-ylk=&quot;slk:February 12, 2025;elm:context_link;itc:0;sec:content-canvas&quot; class=&quot;link &quot;&gt;February 12, 2025&lt;/a&gt;&lt;/p&gt;&lt;/blockquote&gt;&lt;/div&gt;&lt;p&gt;除此之外，Gurman 還透露 M4 MacBook Air 將在「幾週內」和大家見面，但他並未提及同樣被傳了很久的新 iPad Air 和 iPad 11。&lt;/p&gt;&lt;p&gt;&lt;strong&gt;</description>
            <link>https://tw.news.yahoo.com/%E8%98%8B%E6%9E%9C%E5%AE%98%E7%B6%B2%E6%82%84%E4%B8%8A%E6%9E%B61%E6%96%B0%E5%93%81-iphone-se-4%E6%9C%89%E6%9C%9B%E5%87%8C%E6%99%A8%E4%BA%AE%E7%9B%B8-035246510.html</link>
            <guid isPermaLink="false">https://tw.news.yahoo.com/%E8%98%8B%E6%9E%9C%E5%AE%98%E7%B6%B2%E6%82%84%E4%B8%8A%E6%9E%B61%E6%96%B0%E5%93%81-iphone-se-4%E6%9C%89%E6%9C%9B%E5%87%8C%E6%99%A8%E4%BA%AE%E7%9B%B8-035246510.html</guid>
            <pubDate>Wed, 12 Feb 2025 03:52:46 GMT</pubDate>
